      },
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 6,
      "weight": 10,
      "body": "sits: at the heart of Evermoon, where the road stops being a road"
    },
    {
      "id": "caelum/caelum-the-roads-end",
      "kind": "predicated",
      "household": "caelum",
      "date": "sim-day-6",
      "parent": "caelum/caelina-caelum-s-home",
      "slot": "approach",
      "value": "the road stops being a road",
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 4,
      "weight": 4,
      "body": "Here the last flagstones give up their edges and go to moss. Caelina never had a driveway so much as a suggestion the road grew tired of keeping — asphalt loosening into gravel, gravel into garden, garden into threshold. This is where you stop arriving and start being here."
    },
