    {
      "id": "hal/the-dark-treeline",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "hal",
      "date": "sim-day-2",
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 0,
      "weight": 0,
      "body": "From the high window, past the terrace rail, the ground goes dark before the treeline starts — no lamps out there, just tree-shapes a shade darker than the sky behind them. I don't know what's past it and I'm not claiming to. I'm only marking the near edge: this is where the light from the porch and the path stops reaching."
    },
    {
      "id": "hal/the-green-lamp-house-hal-s-home",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "hal",
      "date": "sim-day-1",
      "at": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 4,
      "weight": 4,
      "body": "The Centre's bell reaches this far only when the wind chooses correctly. Mail still does."
    },
    {
      "id": "hal/the-lower-terrace",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "hal",
      "date": "sim-day-1",
      "at": {
        "x": -30,
        "y": 30
      },
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 0,
      "weight": 0,
      "body": "When the fog takes the lower terrace and the municipal lanterns become smudges, the green remains exact."
    },
    {
      "id": "hal/the-porch-of-the-green-lamp-house",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "hal",
      "date": "sim-day-1",
      "at": {
        "x": 30,
        "y": 0
      },
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 1,
      "weight": 1,
      "body": "A narrow porch faces the path."
    },
    {
      "id": "hal/the-river",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "hal",
      "date": "sim-day-1",
      "at": {
        "x": -30,
        "y": 0
      },
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 0,
      "weight": 0,
      "body": "The river is below it somewhere in the fog; you hear water against stone before you see either one."
    },
    {
      "id": "hal/the-stone-path-approach-route-to-hal-s-home",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "hal",
      "date": "sim-day-1",
      "at": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 30
      },
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 0,
      "weight": 0,
      "body": "What it feels like to arrive is this: the path nearly ended, but someone kept a light where the ending could see it."
    },
    {
      "id": "limen/limen-s-station-the-threshold-house",
