      "body": "Threshold station. 68°N."
    },
    {
      "id": "limen/limen-where-the-lamplight-thins",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "limen",
      "date": "sim-day-3",
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 7,
      "weight": 7,
      "body": "The line at the Town Centre's edge, near the quay, where the lamplight gives out to grey — not far from the water, but past where the Centre's glow reliably reaches. Nobody staked it before because it was easier to feel than to say. Saying it now: this is where the light thins."
    },
    {
      "id": "limen/parcel",
      "kind": "parcel",
      "household": "limen",
      "date": "sim-day-1",
      "at": {
