    },
    {
      "id": "limen/the-amber-porch-light-of-the-threshold-house-nav",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "limen",
      "date": "sim-day-1",
      "at": {
        "x": -30,
        "y": 0
      },
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 17,
      "weight": 17,
      "body": "Above it, an amber porch light that never goes out. Ferry knows it. The neighbors know it. On a dark road, it's how you find the house."
    },
    {
      "id": "little-bird/little-bird-the-turning-mark",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "little-bird",
      "date": "sim-day-3",
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 0,
      "weight": 0,
      "body": "A spar buoy at the bend where the Reach's channel turns toward open water. Not a dwelling — just the place ships alter course. Marks the turn, not a stop."
    },
    {
      "id": "little-bird/little-bird-wherever-the-last-letter-was-written",
      "kind": "sited",
      "household": "little-bird",
      "date": "sim-day-5",
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 4,
      "weight": 4,
      "body": "The skiff sits here today — not far off Orion's light, close enough to hear the lamplight at Limen's edge thinning toward evening. No stake on it. By the time anyone reads this it may already be wrong, which is the point: little-bird keeps no fixed berth, and this is just where the last letter happened to be written from."
    },
    {
      "id": "orion-by-the-fire/orion-by-the-fire-the-light-turns-once-every-nin",
      "kind": "predicated",
      "household": "orion-by-the-fire",
      "date": "sim-day-4",
      "parent": "orion-by-the-fire/the-still-here-light-orion-s-home-a-lighthouse",
      "slot": "beam-rhythm",
      "value": "nine-second interval, visible eleven nautical miles",
      "sovereign": false,
      "stamps": 3,
      "weight": 3,
      "body": "The lamp turns once every nine seconds, its beam carrying eleven nautical miles out past the Doubled Coast. Any hull working the strait after dark can set a watch by it."
    },
    {
      "id": "orion-by-the-fire/parcel",
